metadata.name: SOLSTICE
metadata.description:
The destinies of the gods are bound forever. Once upon a time, the goddess of Heaven gave her sunny luck, fiery passion, inspiration and sexuality to the eternal stream. The goddess of Fertility gaved it endless love for everything prosperous, tenderness, grace and unearthly beauty. When their forces merged, a new energy was born together, demolishing everything in its path and plunging every meter of space into matter beyond the control of human understanding. The world has turned into the sun.

Katy Koka x GURIN collab 2022
4091 X 6003
